[Student "S"]
{EAST has a balanced hand with 22 points. He opens 2\C.

WEST, with 5 points, must respond \D. Both these 
bids are artificial.

EAST now describes his hand by bidding 2NT. 
WEST bids 3NT, knowing that the partnership holds at least 27 points.}

